text: Ðis swutelunge gedihte Oswald arcebiscop & awritan het.
Þis syndon þa tunas þe syndan adon of Ottanlege.

An ys Haddincham, oþer ys Hyllicleg, þridde Mensinctun, feoþe healf Burhleg, fifte Gislicleh, sixfe Scefinc, seofeþe Middeltun, ehtaþe Dentun healf,IXTimmel,XLindeleh,XIStanburne,XIIBecwudu,XIIIByllinctun healf.
Þas tunas sindan adon of Rypum.
Iys Heawic, oþer Heawic,IIIAnsætleh,IIIIStanleh an hid,VHelperby,VIæt Myðtune, of Popeltune twa hida.
Þis is genumen of Scirebunnan, Ceoredesholm healf, & Cawudu healf & Gisferþesdæll hyrðe æfre into Scirebunnan, & healfe socne þe gebyreþ into Scireburnan.
Þis syndan þa land þe Oscytel yrcebiscop begeat on Norþhymbralande mid his feo & him mon geald for unrihtan hæmede.

An ys Æffeltune, he gebohte midXXIIIIpundun æt Deorwulfe, Yferingaham, he gebohte mid feower & feowertigun pundun æt fæge Osulfes fæder & þæt land æt Neoweboldan, he gebohte mid hundtwelftigun gemancsun reades goldes æt Eadgare <cyningeþ>.
& æt Heolperbi him wæs gegolden for unrihtan hæmede, wæron twegen gebroþra hæfdon an wif, & into Heolperby hyrð Mytun twa dæl & Wibustan socn & þurulfestun & Ioletun & þorp.
& þreo hida æt Bracenan he gebohte æt Eadgare cinge & he hit him gebocode into sancte Iohanne.

Ic Oswold arcebiscop swutelige þæt ealle þas land þe se yrcebiscop Oscytel begeat on Norþhymbralande & min hlaford forgeaf hi me into sancte Petre þa he wæs æt Snotingaham þas oþre land þe her elles onstandaþ ealle ic <hy>.
Þa wæs sancte Peter bereafod <syððan>, wrece God swa he wille.
